{% layout "base-german" %} {% block content %}
<h1>{{projectName}} - Bericht</h1>

{% comment %}
    For the usage of icons, you can use the script located at /backend/Backend/scripts/getBase64IconForMail.py
    > python3 getBase64IconForMail.py chart-areaspline
{% endcomment %}


<h2>Bericht für den {{dateHumanReadable}}</h2>
<p>Dieser Bericht enthält detaillierte Informationen über die angebotenen Speisen, einschließlich Bewertungen und Kundenkommentare. Sehen Sie sich die Liste unten an, um zu erfahren, was unsere Kunden dazu sagen.</p>
<p>Die folgenden Speisen der Mensen wurden in den Bericht aufgenommen: {{canteen_alias}}</p>

<div>
    {% for food in foods %}
        <div>
            <h3>{{ food.alias }}</h3>
            <div>
                <img src="{{ food.image_url }}" alt="{{ food.alias }}" style="width: 100px; height: 100px;">
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABgAAAAYCAYAAADgdz34AAAAeUlEQVR4nO2W3QqAMAhGPdVF7/+0QY2vq0JGP1QTVvRdOd08oChDkkWqCc3+A+oCAAKGMECUwgHd1QeAn8wk6TDHh0sE+JgkpaIAMxudnU7u7ur9PahvDvYETO44SeqLAsys3XJ+sAfZgN32r/HlV5Etsadal2B4iWYLah5G2Q6o6gAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" alt="chart-bar" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                    Anzahl Bewertungen: {{ food.rating_amount }}
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="chart-areaspline" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                    Durchschnittliche Bewertung: {{ food.rating_average }}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="label" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                    Labels:
                </div>
                <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 20px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; border: 2px solid #ddd;">
                    <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa; background-color: #f2f2f2; border-bottom: 3px solid {{ projectColor }};">
                            Label
                        </th>
                        <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa; background-color: #f2f2f2; border-bottom: 3px solid {{ projectColor }};">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="thumb-up" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                                Anzahl Positiv
                            </div>
                        </th>
                        <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa; background-color: #f2f2f2; border-bottom: 3px solid {{ projectColor }};">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="thumb-down" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                                Anzahl Negativ
                            </div>
                        </th>
                        <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; background-color: #f2f2f2; border-bottom: 3px solid {{ projectColor }};">
                            Anzahl Insgesamt
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                    {% for label in food.labels %}
                        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;">
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa;">{{ label.alias }}</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa;">{{ label.amount_positive }}</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid #aaa;">{{ label.amount_negative }}</td>
                            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: left;">{{ label.amount_total }}</td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>

            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center;">
                    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="comment-multiple" style="width:24px; height:24px; margin-right:8px;">
                    Kommentare:
                </div>
                <ul>
                    {% if food.comments.size > 0 %}
                        {% for comment in food.comments %}
                            <li>{{ comment }}</li>
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% else %}
                        <li>Keine</li>
                    {% endif %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>

<p style="padding-top: 30px">Dies ist ein automatisch generierter Bericht.</p>
{% endblock %}
